
Overview of adv carelessly

The adv carelessly has 3 senses (first 1 from tagged texts)
                                      
1. (1) carelessly, heedlessly -- (without care or concern; "carelessly raised the children's hopes without thinking of their possible disappointment")
2. incautiously, carelessly -- (without caution or prudence; "one unfortunately sees historic features carelessly lost when estates fall into unsympathetic hands")
3. rakishly, raffishly, carelessly -- (in a rakish manner; "she wore her hat rakishly at an angle")
